Commands:
* Format ruby code
* Convert ERB to HAML
* Translate Word with translate.google.com
* Manage mongrel

Snippets
* make_resourceful
* restful_authentication

To install with Git:
  mkdir -p ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
  cd ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
  git clone git@github.com:apetrov/apetrov-bundles.git
  mv apetrov-bundles "Adhoc Bundles.tmbundle"
  osascript -e 'tell app "TextMate" to reload bundles'